'''Denis Višinský''' (born 21 March 2003) is a Czech professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Winger (association football)|winger]] for [[FC Viktoria Plzeň|Viktoria Plzeň]] and the [[Czech Republic national football team|Czech Republic national team]].<ref name="soccerway">{{Soccerway|632402}}</ref>

==Life==
Višinský was born in [[Hořín]], where he also started to play football at the age of three. His family then moved to [[Mělník]].<ref name=sks>{{cite web |title=Podepsat smlouvu se Slavií je velká čest, říká Denis Višinský|url=https://www.slavia.cz/article/17417-Podepsat-smlouvu-se-Slavii-je-velka-cest-rika-Denis-Visinsky|publisher=SK Slavia Prague|language=cs|date=23 March 2020|access-date=2 June 2026}}</ref>

==Career==
Višinský is a youth product of Slavia Prague, having joined their youth academy at the age of six. He signed his first professional contract with them in February 2021.<ref name=sks/> Višinský made his professional debut with Slavia Prague in a 3–0 [[Czech First League]] win over [[FK Mladá Boleslav]] on 14 March 2021.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ca.soccerway.com/matches/2021/03/14/czech-republic/czech-liga/fk-mlada-boleslav/sk-slavia-praha/3331165/|title=Mladá Boleslav vs. Slavia Praha - 14 March 2021|website=Soccerway}}</ref>

On 26 May 2025, Višinský signed a three-year contract with [[FC Viktoria Plzeň|Viktoria Plzeň]] as a free agent.<ref>{{Cite web|last=Sequens|first=Zdeněk|url=https://plzensky.denik.cz/fotbal-prvni-liga/plzen-viktoria-prestup-denis-visinsky-fotbal-chance-liga.html|title=Potvrzeno. Záložník Denis Višinský přestupuje do plzeňské Viktorie|work=[[Deník|Deník.cz]]|publisher=[[Vltava Labe Media]]|language=cs|date=26 May 2025|access-date=26 May 2025}}</ref>

